<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Deployment Failed</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .header { background: #f44336; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; }
        .error-box { background: #ffebee; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-left: 4px solid #f44336; }
        .info-box { background: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-left: 4px solid #666; }
        .code { background: #f8f8f8; padding: 10px; margin: 5px 0; border-radius: 4px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px; overflow-x: auto; }
        .footer { margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; font-size: 0.9em; color: #666; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>‚ùå Deployment Failed</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <div class="error-box">
            <h3>üö® Error Details</h3>
            <p><strong>Error Message:</strong> {{ exception.message }}</p>
            <p><strong>File:</strong> {{ exception.file }}</p>
            <p><strong>Line:</strong> {{ exception.line }}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
            <h3>üìã Request Information</h3>
            <p><strong>IP Address:</strong> {{ request_data.ip }}</p>
            <p><strong>User Agent:</strong> {{ request_data.user_agent }}</p>
            <p><strong>Timestamp:</strong> {{ request_data.timestamp|date('Y-m-d H:i:s') }}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
            <h3>üîç Stack Trace</h3>
            <pre class="code">{{ exception.traceAsString }}</pre>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>‚ö†Ô∏è Your deployment has failed and requires attention.</p>
            <p><strong>Next Steps:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Check the error message and stack trace above</li>
                <li>Review the deployment logs for more details</li>
                <li>Fix the issue and retry the deployment</li>
                <li>Contact the development team if needed</li>
            </ul>
            <p><small>This is an automated message from your deployment system.</small></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 